Class Collectible

java.lang.Object
city.cs.engine.Body
city.cs.engine.DynamicBody
game.entities.Collectible
public class Collectible extends city.cs.engine.DynamicBody
Represents a collectible item in the game world.

This class extends DynamicBody to create an item that can be collected by the player or other entities. It uses a circular shape and displays a coin animation image.

  • Field Details

    • COLLECTIBLE_SHAPE

      private static final city.cs.engine.Shape COLLECTIBLE_SHAPE
      A circular shape defining the physical boundary for the collectible.

      The radius of the circle is set to 0.5 units.

    • COLLECTIBLE_IMAGE

      private static final city.cs.engine.BodyImage COLLECTIBLE_IMAGE
      A coin GIF image used as the visual representation of the collectible.

      The image is scaled to a height of 1 unit.
